lead_paragraph: ROSE--Dr. Murray F.,95. Kind, adored and revered. For many, he was everything. His love of life and contributions will never be forgotten. Survived by his beloved wife Karel, five sons, eight grandchildren. Memorial service at Temple Beth-El, Great Neck, NY, May 26th, 12 noon. 1/3

headline.main: Paid Notice: Deaths  ROSE, DR. MURRAY F.
